Modern marketing approaches, trends.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to improve and develop knowledge and skills related to the basic concepts and methods of marketing and management.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon the completion of the course the student: 1) use basic marketing management terms and concepts, and understand the theoretical and practical issues of marketing management in enterprises; 2) understand the specifics of marketing and be able to compile marketing plans based on these; 3) analyse the marketing management of an organization (company) and create a suitable marketing strategy for a new service; 4) conduct a marketing analysis of the company and its environment to critically assess the risks associated with the implementation of the marketing strategy and the suitability of competition strategies; 5) know marketing trends and how to take advantage of these in service development.
